medicationCodeableConcept.text: Docusate Sodium 100 mg Cap 1 capsule by mouth twice a day
Metoclopramide 10 mg Tab (Reglan) 1 tablet by mouth every 8 hours as needed for nausea
Ondansetron HCl 8 mg Tab (Zofran) 1 tablet by mouth every 12 hours
Warfarin 5 mg two tablets by mouth daily except 1.5 tabs on Monday and Friday.
Zyprexa 20 mg by mouth twice a day
zolpidem 10 mg Tab (Ambien) 1 tablet by mouth every evening at bedtime as needed for insomnia
Losartan 25 mg Tab (Cozaar) 1 tablet by mouth daily
Tamoxifen 20 mg po daily for a total of 5 years
Dexamethasone 4 mg Tab 1 tablet by mouth twice a day
hydrocodone-acetaminophen 10 mg-500 mg Tab (Lortab) 1 tablet by mouth every 6 hours as needed for pain
Oxycodone-Acetaminophen 5 mg-325 mg Tab (Percocet) 2 tablets by mouth every 6 hours as needed
Claritin 10 mg by mouth as needed for allergies
lactulose 10 gram/15 mL Oral Soln 30 milliliters by mouth every evening at bedtime as needed for constipation
Lovenox 100 mg/mL Sub-Q Syringe 1 syringe subcutaneously every 12 hours for 3 days
Neulasta 6 mg/0.6 mL Sub-Q Syringe 1 syringe subcutaneously one time only
Prochlorperazine Maleate 5 mg Tab 1 tablet by mouth every 8 hours as needed for nausea
lorazepam 0.5 mg Tab (Ativan) 1 tablet by mouth every 8 hours as needed for muscle spasms/anxiety
